snippet.title: Battle Talent - Official Multiplayer Update Launch Trailer | Upload VR Showcase
snippet.description: Battle Talent is a physics-based roguelite sword-fighting game developed by CyDream. The Multiplayer update for the game brings the ability for friends to join together and slay hordes of enemies side by side. The Multiplayer update for Battle Talent is available now for Steam VR and Meta Quest.
